<div class="homepage-job-reviews-description-content">
  <div class="container">
    <hr class="narrow" />
    <div class="sub-group">
      <%= image_tag 'man-white-truck.jpg'%>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-group">
      <p>Big Truck Driving Jobs is ready to get you rolling on the open road. Whether you want an OTR truck driving job or you are looking for local trucking jobs, now that you have your CDL, we've got you covered. Thanks to our convenient, 100 percent free and secure process we will help you find the dream truck driver job. Save time and energy with our exceptional online application system that lets you apply once to as many trucking jobs as you want!</p>

      <h3>Our Convenient Job Search Process and Online Application</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Apply for trucking jobs online using our 100 percent free online application.</li>
        <li>Big Truck Driving Jobs search among top paying trucking companies and driver employers.</li>
        <li>We present you with truck driving companies that match your trucking background, such as your truck driving history, CDL class, and work experience.</li>
        <li>Meanwhile you can find out more about their company, benefits for truckers, jobs available and the types of truckers they are hiring.</li>
        <li>Sit back and wait for trucking companies to approve your application and to contact you with a job.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Truckers Who Want Big Truck Driving Jobs</h3>

      <p>Whether you are a rookie driver with no driving experience or OTR trucker with 20 years of experience we can find a job that you are suited for in our online database. We have jobs for:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Flatbed Trucking Jobs</li>
        <li>Heavy Equipment Haulers</li>
        <li>Dry Van Trucking Jobs</li>
        <li>Refrigerated Trucking Jobs</li>
        <li>Regional Truck Driving Jobs</li>
        <li>Tanker Jobs</li>
        <li>Auto Hauling Jobs</li>
      </ul>

      <p>...just to name a few. Owner operators and those looking to drive leased trucks come to us to find trucking jobs. We work with dispatchers and driver employers who need to find short term drivers, as well as national trucking companies who want full-time truck drivers fast.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

